description.fr: {CharacterName:708} et son fils {CharacterName:654} ont pour mission de repousser tout ce qui pourrait sortir de la faille apparue sur Astrub. Toute aide est la bienvenue.
description.en: {CharacterName:708} and his son {CharacterName:654}'s mission is to push back anything that might come out of the rift that appeared in Astrub. Any help at all would be welcome.
description.es: {CharacterName:708} y su hijo {CharacterName:654} tienen la misión de repeler todo lo que salga de la falla que ha aparecido en Astrub. Toda ayuda es bienvenida.
description.de: {CharacterName:708} und sein Sohn {CharacterName:654} sollen alles zurückschlagen, was sich aus dem Riss in Astrub heraustraut. Jede Hilfe ist gern gesehen.
description.pt: {CharacterName:708} e seu filho {CharacterName:654} têm como missão mandar de volta tudo o que sai da fenda que surgiu em Astrub. Toda ajuda é bem-vinda.

descriptionFinished.fr: Après un tête-à-tête entre père et fils, {CharacterName:708} et {CharacterName:654} sont plus déterminés que jamais à garder leur faille. Les Shushus n'ont aucune chance contre eux\_!
descriptionFinished.en: After a father-son talk, {CharacterName:708} and {CharacterName:654} are more determined than ever to guard their rift. The Shushus don't stand a chance against them!
descriptionFinished.es: Tras un cara a cara entre padre e hijo, {CharacterName:708} y {CharacterName:654} están más decididos que nunca a vigilar su falla. ¡Los fab'huritus no tienen ninguna posibilidad contra ellos!
descriptionFinished.de: Nachdem sich Vater und Sohn unter vier Augen unterhalten haben, sind {CharacterName:708} und {CharacterName:654} entschlossener denn je, ihren Riss zu beschützen. Die Shushus haben gegen die beiden keine Chance!
descriptionFinished.pt: Depois de uma conversinha entre pai e filho, {CharacterName:708} e {CharacterName:654} estão mais determinados que nunca a vigiar a fenda. Os Shushus não têm nenhuma chance contra eles!
